Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:05.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 赤司 赤司！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:06.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,平人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,平人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚听到平人的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:33.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,袤然世界 欲噬尽 无明滚滚蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:39.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,斯人祈愿 尽合一 拥黑暗于心间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:43.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但得救赎 抑或福音 世间遍播散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫 给这一切都画上一个句号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,连同我们的罪业一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:58.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明暗相隔 此厢亦有期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:03.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但得尽驱黑暗 纵两败俱伤 无悔无怨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,至福之光 愿终可 遍撒广阔世间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,心各有志 纵殊途同归 难避一战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无边曙光 终耀无明黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫 我来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:17.03,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}にじんでる歩道橋のらくがき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:28.25,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}置いてかれた自転車　誰かの帰りを待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:33.42,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}認めて　ただ存在を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.05,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕こそがオリジナル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.55,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あるいはそのレプリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.01,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らの証明はどこにある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.85,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人類の欠点は　見えもしないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:53.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛とか絆とか信じられること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.03,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕の罪はうたがったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.20,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}差し伸べられた君の右手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.16,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}初めて見たヒカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:13.21,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らは———
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:17.03,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,岁月流转　天桥涂鸦终归消散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:28.25,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,静置难安　单车默待谁人与共还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:33.42,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,坦然直面　存在世间　身外孑然一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.05,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却难断　吾乃本源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.55,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,抑或水月云烟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.01,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,孰真孰幻　吾等安辩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.85,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,人心缺点难免　未曾得见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:53.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,爱与羁绊　却坚信依然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.03,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心疑难掩　吾罪何堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.20,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,与君右手紧牵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.16,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,唯慨叹　光明初现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:13.21,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,吾等只盼……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:33.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1029,1029)\pos(1316,700)}第二十二话\N交相辉映
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里只有我们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和当初离开读岛时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在岛上一起玩耍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个本是一体的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本来就不该分开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志你从小就『这样吧』『那样吧』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,老是在说你想怎样怎样 烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:04:00.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目么整天苍蝇似的围着我\N『要做什么啊』『要怎么做啊』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了 你们竟还有脸来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来的不是赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我去死吧 你和笹目一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧 全都去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:38.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫你好奇怪啊 你的心里好像不太正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恨我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让我们去死 是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来杀我吧 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧 皆志你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是下不了手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那不是你心里真正的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:45.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你不要过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:56.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就看一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 你说看就看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖让我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手呀皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想要拯救你的啊 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 无明领域竟然停止扩张了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说皆志他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:46.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然原因不明但暂时稳定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}为什么要这样做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快复原啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没做错啊 这不怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是听话照做了而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又不是我一个人做的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起做的孩子他们都逃走了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:17.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来呀 笹目 皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉的人们在生气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这排山倒海的愤怒和怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,催升了无明石大人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么能怪我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个回岛上去好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家四散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒 怨恨 悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这十年来你都是这样一个人担掠受怕的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 像那时一样合而为一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他也一定会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果所有人都能合而为一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就再也不会有误解了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也就都会幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫和赤司也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:21.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志你根本就没明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:38.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为大家联结在一起才得不到幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:44.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和这些游荡在这里一直责难我的人联结吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:50.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己心中的黑暗催升了无明石大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这群肮脏的存在却要来责难我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要和这种人联结在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:03.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的人们也不希望无明领域再继续扩大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我管不了了 你们都是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖沉沦在这惩罚的痛苦中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要比我所承受的要更加更加痛苦才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明领域又开始扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且速度还在急剧上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再有三分钟就会到达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:45.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全员撤退 这要被无明领域吞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别掉队 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:09:59.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,注意前方障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:10.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岩人 来夏 照顾好笠音姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和艾米露维持共信就不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:28.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,马上要和无明领域接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这精神侵蚀也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还好吧 岩人 来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥现在又不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不能共信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是无法从这幻象中脱身了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呀艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,除我之外大家都被无明领域困住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁能听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岩人 来夏 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:12.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,自说自话就进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要来扰我孤独啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管谁快点回应我一下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:33.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…神木？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候出现在这的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里原本是别的树啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又能做到些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:36.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然速度有所下降 但无明领域仍在稳步扩大中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,日本以外的国家也开始在探讨无明领域的对策了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,留给我们的时间也不是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道神木能坚持多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但话说回来怎么会在这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:59.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是神木在这里 而是变成了神木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓神木 是原本普通的植物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:08.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为能在无明领域里生存而主动变化出的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:13.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,两棵树通过互相联结共同抵抗尸钢化的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这和界联系统是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能了解其实现方法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就可以防止尸钢化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:22.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多亏了你呢 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？啊…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定要努力解救艾米露和笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这下完全变成无明领域内的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经让全员都携带了神木果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过效果还不能确定 断不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是希望能把骸从无明领域中心地带拖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说和之前的诱饵作战一样咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这次的诱饵就拜托赤司你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,根据以往的记录来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司只要有神木果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是进入无明领域中心地带也很可能不受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:13.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和平人的共信仍需要进行进一步的分析确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定赤司有着目前未知的共信能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且和骸的战斗经验也是最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:28.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在将骸引出后赤司转乘银和大家一起发起总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难说百分之百会成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是眼下最可行的方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,由我去的话可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:42.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是突然唱哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概由MA-Vess去的话才最靠谱吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前来夏对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:56.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,『要为自己问心无愧而战』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她说得有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道艾米露也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是逃回来的话应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也就只会逃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那就将计划改为围绕真亚梦展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 我真没想到你会主动请缨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:38.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:43.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一向满足于无所事事专心写小说的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟会说出那样的话 真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是艾米露还活在我心中 受她的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是你亲囗说出的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:57.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,出击准备已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,全机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,Vess掩护黑前往突入点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦 别掉队哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,另一边也围过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:24.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧去死吧去死吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,距到达突入点还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里全部来个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 真亚梦 艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明物语 亦终临 曲终人散之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等之力 定使其 落幕此时今日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,千里足下 吾等篇章 亦于此奏响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,纵然渺小 坚信定有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:18:59.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,黑已与骸接触
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在开的要是MA-Vess的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,又来 你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:22.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司…赤司…赤司…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在和赤司共信？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在叫我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 原来是想要界联系统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要么我来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:41.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会强行共信的啊 就像艾米露那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:48.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏入当初的资料里倒是也认为平人有着很高的共信能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底还要这样到什么时候啊 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再躲下去骸就要回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 再不出去就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:08.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像为保护栖息其上的生物而变化的神木一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能有所改变的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 会有所改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你追得上就来追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来追我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,动…动不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:01.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能就这样惨淡退场啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要把骸带到大家那里去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一个人还在注视着我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界也会看起来不再那么糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你 艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米露和我的故事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会迎来幸福圆满的结局的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快把这家伙带到大家那里去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You lose your mind, you crash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.06,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.94,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.90,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.57,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.49,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.66,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.28,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.67,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.04,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.34,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.92,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.38,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.76,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.47,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.93,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.48,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.27,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.11,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.65,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.12,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.95,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
